channel.title: ***3rd Model *** Gilded Black Dragon Platebody
channel.description:
Hey this is my third model well I guess not a model but I recolored a bronze plate body made by Jagex, added some spikes, took a beautiful cape [btw who made that if you could tell me who did I'd be happy to put him in the credits] and merged it with this, and took a few things off... So yeah Thanks please no flaming as it is my third model... But constructive critisism would help a whole lot I didn't much on my last model [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,493055.msg3604677.html#msg3604677]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,493055.msg3604677.html#msg3604677[/url] So please just comment and like it! :cool: :D :cool:
